                    <div class="row g-4">
                        <div class="col-md-12">
                            <div class="card process-card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                                <div class="card-body p-4">
                                    <h4 class="fw-bold"><span class="badge bg-primary rounded-circle me-2">1</span> Import Learning Outcomes</h4>
                                    <p class="mb-0">Instructors import and customize a list of about 40 specific learning outcomes for their course (e.g., Calculus I). Our platform makes it easy to modify existing skill lists or create new ones.</p>
                                </div>
