                                    <h4 class="fw-bold"><span class="badge bg-primary rounded-circle me-2">2</span> Create Weekly Assessments</h4>
                                    <p class="mb-0">Each week, faculty use our app to generate comprehensive exams covering all skills introduced so far. The app allows faculty to select challenging questions from the problem bank for each skill (or create new ones), creating personalized exams in just 20 minutes of faculty time.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-12">
                            <div class="card process-card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
